#

Savory Pork Tenderloin with Herb-infused Gravy and Garlic Mashed Potatoes

$20
650 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

Main CourseComfort FoodGourmet

Description

Juicy pork tenderloin served with a rich herb-infused gravy and creamy garlic mashed potatoes, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • Pork Tenderloin: 1 lb
  • Garlic: 4 cloves
  • Fresh Rosemary: 2 sprigs
  • Fresh Thyme: 2 sprigs
  • Chicken Broth: 2 cups
  • Heavy Cream: 1/2 cup
  • Butter: 4 tbsp
  • Potatoes: 2 lbs
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
